# .clang-format
---
BasedOnStyle: LLVM # or “Google”, “Chromium”, etc.—pick your favorite fallback
IndentWidth: 4 # logical indent level (clang-format still needs this even when using tabs)
TabWidth: 4 # how wide each tab is rendered
UseTab: ForIndentation # emit real tabs for leading indentation only
UseCRLF: false # false → LF, true → CRLF  (requires clang-format 12+)
